tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Outreach_Programs ( 
  program_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, 
  program_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
  target_community VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, 
  outreach_date DATE, 
  outreach_status BOOLEAN 
);

CREATE TABLE Outreach_Programs (
    program_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name VARCHAR(255),
    outreach_date DATE,
    community_id UUID,
    effectiveness_rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE Community_Health_Status (
    community_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    community_name VARCHAR(255),
    outreach_program_id UUID,
    health_status VARCHAR(255),
    outreach_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE OutreachPrograms (
  program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  program_name VARCHAR(255),
  community_target VARCHAR(255),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE ProgramParticipants (
  participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  program_id INT,
  participant_name VARCHAR(255),
  community VARCHAR(255),
  enrollment_date DATE,
  completion_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE outreach_programs (
  program_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  program_name VARCHAR(50),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  outreach_location VARCHAR(100),
  target_community VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE program_participants (
  participant_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  program_id UUID REFERENCES outreach_programs(program_id),
  participant_name VARCHAR(50),
  contact_number VARCHAR(15),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE participant_feedback (
  feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_id UUID REFERENCES program_participants(participant_id),
  feedback_date DATE,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE program_performance (
  performance_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  program_id UUID REFERENCES outreach_programs(program_id),
  performance_date DATE,
  num_participants INT,
  efficacy_rating INT,
  success_metric VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Outreach_Programs (
  program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  program_name VARCHAR(50),
  program_description TEXT,
  target_community VARCHAR(100),
  program_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Participants (
  participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_name VARCHAR(50),
  participant_age INT,
  participant_gender VARCHAR(10),
  program_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (program_id) REFERENCES Outreach_Programs(program_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Engagement_Records (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_id INT,
  engagement_date DATETIME,
  engagement_type VARCHAR(50),
  engagement_notes TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (participant_id) REFERENCES Participants(participant_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Health_Outcomes (
  outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_id INT,
  outcome_date DATE,
  outcome_metrics VARCHAR(100),
  outcome_notes TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (participant_id) REFERENCES Participants(participant_id)
);
